 &lt;div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none"&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;Momma bought a Christmas gift for you. She says it&amp;rsquo;s something you love! But Christmas is like more than 6 months away :/ Try to peek in and find out what the gift is, before the Christmas eve ;)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Want a byte?</title><link>https://ctf.jonghan.xyz/posts/2022/standcon-2022/reverse/want-a-byte/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jun 2022 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ctf.jonghan.xyz/posts/2022/standcon-2022/reverse/want-a-byte/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;a href="#description" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Link to this section"&gt;&lt;svg class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"&gt;&lt;g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
 &lt;blockquote
