 &gt;
 &lt;div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none"&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;Scrolling through my projects, I found some old project code. I remember this code had some &amp;ldquo;backdoors&amp;rdquo;. But since I mistakenly deleted utils.py, now I cannot understand my own code! Can you help me make sense out of it? You will be rewarded with a flag for your help.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>